The Aesthetic Tech Forum was a huge hit this past week, and I had the great honor of being the emcee for the fourth year in a row. This year, I helped curate some amazing speakers and keynote interviews to shed light on where the innovation in aesthetics is! Even more exciting is my role on the board of directors @octaneoc, the amazing med tech organization that hosts this and many other world class signature events. I look forward to advising Launchpad companies through their startup accelerator and advising the affiliated Visionary Venture Fund looking to invest in aesthetic tech in a major way over the coming years! Thanks to these amazing speakers for sharing their insight! #octane #atf #aesthetictechforum #drz #emcee #becauseitsfun #bod #boardofdirectors #ilooklikeaplasticsurgeon #especiallywheniamtheemcee #plasticsurgeon #siliconvalley

Like many mothers, Dr. Z sought to rebuild her self-confidence and physical strength after having a baby. And it was through EmSculpt & @oneyogasource that she was able to do so. This is why we’re teaming up with YogaSource to bring you a 6 month Online Core Program and an opportunity to take it to the next level with our Enhance Program. The Enhance Program will allow you to experience EmSculpt, an innovative treatment for building muscle and sculpting the body, the perfect ENHANCEMENT to your Core Program.

To kick off our new Enhance Program, everyone who enrolls in YogaSource’s Core Program will gain access to:
🤍 A complimentary EmSculpt trial
🤍 A complimentary skincare consultation
🤍 Enhance-ment Packages (More to come!)

LINK IN BIO TO ENROLL. An email will be sent out on 2/2 to everyone enrolled about scheduling your EmSculpt trial & skincare consult.
